- For the purpose of this question, 'top tracks' refers to those with the highest popularity scores within their respective genres and decades; 
- A 'genre's average popularity' is the mean of the popularity scores of all tracks within that genre in a given decade; 
- The 'genre rank' is determined by the genre's average popularity within a decade, with 1 being the highest; 
- A 'decade' is a period of 10 years, e.g., 2000-2009, 2010-2019.
